summary: This is a Sprint invoice for a subpoena compliance request from the FBI's West Palm Beach office, detailing charges for call detail reports and reprints. It indicates law enforcement investigation activity involving telecommunications records.

events.title: Sprint Invoice Issued for FBI Subpoena
events.description: Sprint issued an invoice to the FBI's West Palm Beach office for subpoena compliance services including call detail reports and reprints.

locations: 500 S. Flagler Drive West Palm Beach FL 33401
keyFacts: The FBI's West Palm Beach office was conducting an investigation requiring telecommunications records from Sprint in November 2006.
Sprint charged $205 for subpoena compliance services including call detail reports and reprints.
The invoice references Sprint Case 2M-149246, indicating a specific law enforcement request.
This document shows financial billing for investigative work related to what appears to be an active FBI case.
